Description: Music Man is a premier guitar maker...and this beautiful Luke guitar in a deep and rich blue...is a perfect example of their 'custom shop look and feel' at standard pricing. The color is a very deep and beautiful blue...and the neck and headstock have birds eye maple with a rosewood fingerboard. The pickup configuration has 2 EMG single coils and 1 EMG hum bucker in the bridge...so this guitar can play anything from clean jazz...to the heaviest of heavy metal. This guitar is part of a private collection from an old customer...with very little playtime...but there are two scrapes on the back of the body and pick marks on the front of the body. You will need to have the guitar setup to your personal play style after arrival. I will include a brand new 9 volt battery before shipment.
